                      <SHORT-NAME>CddIpcMainFunctionReadPeriod</SHORT-NAME>
                      <DESC>
                        <L-2 L="EN">This parameter describes the period for cyclic call to Cdd_Ipc_MainFunction_Read. Unit is seconds.</L-2>
                      </DESC>
